'''Greg''' is a worker in a skyscraper that caught on fire.

==History==
Greg was on the floor when the fire started in the skyscraper. He tried to make a run for it, but got trapped and was burned. He was upset because he was supposed to have left early. Ben told him it was a good day and he'd be able to go home to his kid that night.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
He was supposed to pick his daughter up early, but got called into a work thing, so he cancelled.

==Career==
He works in an office in a skyscraper in downtown Seattle.
